id: pm-ax7z
title: "Convert docs/examples extensions to TypeScript-first (starter-extension, policy-restricted-extension)"
description: "Honor ADR pm-2c28 for the committed docs/examples extensions, which are still authored in plain JavaScript (docs/examples/starter-extension/index.js 199L all-9-capabilities showcase + docs/examples/policy-restricted-extension/index.js). Add index.ts source authored against the SDK types, keep the compiled index.js the loader/tests import (mirror first-party packages/pm-*), and wire type-checking (add docs/examples/**/*.ts to a packages-style tsconfig include). The starter-extension test docstring already (incorrectly) claims TS authorship. Deferred from the scaffolder PR to keep that PR focused on the generator + SDK primitives + docs reframe."
